<div id="header">
	<!-- Intro Text -->
	<div class="header-call">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="small-12 medium-11 medium-centered columns text-center">
				<h1 class="animated fadeInUp">Creating Ruby on Rails Applications that are <em>Minimal</em>, <em>Usable</em>, and <em>Persuasive</em>.</h1>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="off-white" id="home-why-sign-up">
	<div class="big-spacer">
		<div class="row">
			<h1 class="text-center">Why Sign Up</h1>
			<div class="medium-spacer-top medium-spacer-bottom">
				<div class="row">
					<div class="small-12 medium-6 columns">
						<%= image_tag 'code.jpg', class: "border" %>
					</div>
					<div class="small-12 medium-6 columns">
						<h4>Bring your ideas to life. Learn to program.</h4>
						<p>You have a great idea. Do you know how to <strong>create that idea</strong> online? If not, I'll teach you how.</p>
						<p><%= link_to "Sign Up Now", "#", "data-reveal-id" => "sign-up-modal", class: "pink-link-center" %></p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="big-spacer-top small-spacer-bottom">
				<div class="row">
					<div class="small-12 medium-6 medium-push-6 columns">
						<%= image_tag 'psychology.png' %>
					</div>
					<div class="small-12 medium-6 medium-pull-6 columns">
						<h4>Make Website People Love to Use</h4>
						<p>Once you've learned to program <em><strong>you realize instantly how important the interface is</strong></em>. How to make an interface that the user loves.  One that is beautiful, minimal, easy to use, and speaks to the user.</p>
						<p><em><strong>Making an impact online is so much more than creating a website.</strong></em></p>
						<p><%= link_to "Sign up to now", "#", "data-reveal-id" => "sign-up-modal", class: "pink-link-center" %> and learn the technology <strong><em>and</em></strong> the psychology behind making amazing websites.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
					
					<div class="small-spacer row">
						<div class="small-12 medium-6 medium-centered columns">
							<% if user_signed_in? %>
								<%= link_to	"What Do You Want To Learn?", new_feedback_path, class: "button expand button-pink" %>
							<% else %>
								<%= link_to "Sign Up For Free", "#", "data-reveal-id" => "sign-up-modal", class: "button expand button-pink" %>
							<% end %>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>


<div class="big-spacer">
	<div class="row text-center">
		<h1>What You Get By Signing Up</h1>
		<div class="small-spacer">
			<div class="small-12 medium-6 columns">
				<div class="what-you-get">
					<%= image_tag("free-resources.png") %>
				</div>
				<p>Every web project will need access to certain resources, such as high-quality images, usability test templates, excellent designs, and so on.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="small-12 medium-6 offset-1 columns">
				<div class="what-you-get">
					<%= image_tag("step-by-step.png") %>
				</div>
				<p>Learn, through guided step-by-step training, how to create beautiful and persuasive web apps in ruby on rails, even if you're not a designer or developer.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>


<div class="gray-strip">
	<div class="small-spacer">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="small-12 medium-6 medium-centered columns">
				<% if user_signed_in? %>
					<%= link_to	"Thank You For Signing Up", training_path, class: "button expand button-pink" %>
				<% else %>
					<%= link_to "Sign up, for free!", "#", "data-reveal-id" => "sign-up-modal", class: "button expand button-pink" %>
				<% end %>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="footer">
	<footer>
		<div class="row text-center">
			<div class="small-6 small-centered columns">
